<plot>A two-man alpine climbing up a new route on Gyachung Kang in Tibet, with partner Bruce Miller. "Alpine-style" climbers believe in earning their summits. Two climbers, without support or fixed camps, attempting remote, difficult routes. They risk everything against the elements, relying on experience, each other and their luck. As an introduction, the film also documents two earlier alpine style climbs.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?639080</url></doc>
